How to generate flow charts from the source in this directory
=============================================================

1. Install the Graphviz software from http://www.graphviz.org

2. Make sure the dot command is in the shell's path.

3. Run dot gv to generate and display the flow charts respectively:

   X=coordinateRemoteCopy; dot -Tps $X.dot > $X.ps; gv $X.ps
